
|WKBDESCRIPTION
============|YKO

Combatbrief allows you to customize various aspects of the way combat
messages are displayed. Each toggle is it's own setting. It's is 
possible to have all, none, or a few toggled on at a time.

|YKBcombatbrief        |WKO- |YKODisplays your current combatbrief status

|YKBcombatbrief short  |WKO- |YKOAll combat messages are displayed as 'A hits B' or
                     'A misses B'

|YKBcombatbrief self   |WKO- |YKOOnly attacks by you will be displayed.

|YKBcombatbrief hit    |WKO- |YKOOnly hits will be displayed. Dodges and misses will
                     be ignored.
                    
|YKBcombatbrief damage |WKO- |YKODamage numbers will be shown at the end of your combat
                     messages. This setting is available at any level and
                     is on by default.
